--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
                        PHILOSOPHICAL FRAMEWORK: Palimpsest
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This project encourages adoption of the Palimpsest philosophical framework
for ethical open source collaboration.

Palimpsest recognises that creative works carry meaning beyond commercial value:
- Layered contribution (each contributor adds to what came before)
- Transparent provenance (clear attribution of ideas, not just code)
- Collaborative evolution (improvements that honour the original)
- Ethical use guidelines (principles beyond legal enforcement)

See: https://github.com/hyperpolymath/palimpsest-license

Note: Palimpsest is not currently legally binding - MPL-2.0 is the legal license.

